This is a Django application allowing to index and then browse instalations of
Solaris packages.

Populating the database
-----------------------

Get the output of pkginfo.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
solarisbox=fqdn.yourdomain.com
ssh ${solarisbox} pkginfo -l > ${solarisbox}.pkginfo
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Execute Django shell

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./manage.py shell
from solaris.packages import MachineEnumerator
me = MachineEnumerator("fqdn.yourdomain.com")
me.Executify()
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
